"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The former US Secretary of State testified that she did not know about Epstein's crimes. She also said President Trump should be questioned about this.\",            \"english_title\": \"Former Secretary Testifies\",            \"translated_version\": \"La ex Secretaria de Estado de EE.UU. dijo que no sab\u00eda sobre los cr\u00edmenes de Epstein. Tambi\u00e9n dijo que el Presidente Trump deber\u00eda ser preguntado sobre esto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ex Secretaria Testifica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Donald Trump wants to annex Greenland, and this issue is likely to be a big topic in the election campaign.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump and Greenland\",            \"translated_version\": \"Donald Trump quiere anexar Groenlandia, y este tema probablemente ser\u00e1 importante en la campa\u00f1a electoral.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump y Groenlandia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Geneva, there are indirect talks happening as a last effort to reach a nuclear agreement, but it is not clear if they will succeed.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nuclear Talks in Geneva\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Ginebra, hay conversaciones indirectas como \u00faltimo esfuerzo para llegar a un acuerdo nuclear, pero no est\u00e1 claro si tendr\u00e1n \u00e9xito.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones Nucleares en Ginebra\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Greece, a surveillance software called Predator was used to spy on 87 people, and this incident is being called 'Greece's Watergate'.\",            \"english_title\": \"Greece's Surveillance Scandal\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Grecia, un software de vigilancia llamado Predator fue usado para espiar a 87 personas, y este incidente se llama 'Watergate de Grecia'.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Esc\u00e1ndalo de Vigilancia en Grecia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israeli forces stopped Palestinian ambulances while a 14-year-old was bleeding for at least 45 minutes.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ambulances Blocked\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las fuerzas israel\u00edes detuvieron ambulancias palestinas mientras un ni\u00f1o de 14 a\u00f1os sangraba por al menos 45 minutos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ambulancias Bloqueadas\"        }    ]}"